var book = {
	"name": "Galatians",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29042A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29042A\"></sup>apostle—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29042B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29042B\"></sup>not from men nor through man, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29042C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29042C\"></sup>through Jesus Christ and God the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29042D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29042D\"></sup>who raised him from the dead—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29043E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29043E\"></sup>the brothers who are with me,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29043F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29043F\"></sup>the churches of Galatia:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29044G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29044G\"></sup>Grace to you and peace <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29044H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29044H\"></sup>from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29045I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29045I\"></sup>who gave himself for our sins to deliver us from the present <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29045J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29045J\"></sup>evil age, according to the will of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29045K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29045K\"></sup>our God and Father,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to whom be the glory forever and ever. Amen.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I am astonished that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29047L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29047L\"></sup>so quickly deserting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29047M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29047M\"></sup>him who called you in the grace of Christ and are turning to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29047N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29047N\"></sup>a different gospel—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29048O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29048O\"></sup>not that there is another one, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29048P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29048P\"></sup>there are some who trouble you and want to distort the gospel of Christ.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But even if we or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29049Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29049Q\"></sup>an angel from heaven should preach to you a gospel contrary to the one we preached to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29049R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29049R\"></sup>let him be accursed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As we have said before, so now I say again: If anyone is preaching to you a gospel contrary to the one you received, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29050S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29050S\"></sup>let him be accursed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For am I now seeking the approval of man, or of God? Or am I trying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29051T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29051T\"></sup>to please man? If I were still trying to please man, I would not be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29051U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29051U\"></sup>servant of Christ.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29052V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29052V\"></sup>I would have you know, brothers, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29052W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29052W\"></sup>the gospel that was preached by me is not man's gospel.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29053X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29053X\"></sup>For I did not receive it from any man, nor was I taught it, but I received it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29053Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29053Y\"></sup>through a revelation of Jesus Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For you have heard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29054Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29054Z\"></sup>my former life in Judaism, how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29054AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29054AA\"></sup>I persecuted the church of God violently and tried to destroy it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And I was advancing in Judaism beyond many of my own age among my people, so extremely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29055AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29055AB\"></sup>zealous was I for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29055AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29055AC\"></sup>the traditions of my fathers.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29056AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29056AD\"></sup>who had set me apart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29056AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29056AE\"></sup>before I was born, and who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29056AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29056AF\"></sup>called me by his grace,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>was pleased to reveal his Son to me, in order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29057AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29057AG\"></sup>that I might preach him among the Gentiles, I did not immediately consult with anyone;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>nor did I go up to Jerusalem to those who were apostles before me, but I went away into Arabia, and returned again to Damascus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29059AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29059AH\"></sup>after three years I went up to Jerusalem to visit Cephas and remained with him fifteen days.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I saw none of the other apostles except James <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29060AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29060AI\"></sup>the Lord's brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>(In what I am writing to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29061AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29061AJ\"></sup>before God, I do not lie!)",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29062AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29062AK\"></sup>Then I went into the regions of Syria and Cilicia.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And I was still unknown in person to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29063AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29063AL\"></sup>the churches of Judea that are in Christ.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They only were hearing it said, “He who used to persecute us is now preaching the faith he once tried to destroy.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And they glorified God because of me."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Then after fourteen years I went up again to Jerusalem with Barnabas, taking Titus along with me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I went up because of a revelation and set before them (though privately before those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29067A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29067A\"></sup>who seemed influential) the gospel that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29067B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29067B\"></sup>I proclaim among the Gentiles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29067C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29067C\"></sup>in order to make sure I was not running or had not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29067D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29067D\"></sup>run in vain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But even Titus, who was with me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29068E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29068E\"></sup>was not forced to be circumcised, though he was a Greek.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29069F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29069F\"></sup>Yet because of false brothers secretly brought in—who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29069G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29069G\"></sup>slipped in to spy out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29069H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29069H\"></sup>our freedom that we have in Christ Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29069I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29069I\"></sup>so that they might bring us into slavery—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>to them we did not yield in submission even for a moment, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29070J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29070J\"></sup>the truth of the gospel might be preserved for you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And from those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29071K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29071K\"></sup>who seemed to be influential (what they were makes no difference to me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29071L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29071L\"></sup>God shows no partiality)—those, I say, who seemed influential <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29071M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29071M\"></sup>added nothing to me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>On the contrary, when they saw that I had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29072N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29072N\"></sup>entrusted with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29072O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29072O\"></sup>the gospel to the uncircumcised, just as Peter had been entrusted with the gospel to the circumcised",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>(for he who worked through Peter for his apostolic ministry to the circumcised worked also through me for mine to the Gentiles),",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and when James and Cephas and John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29074P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29074P\"></sup>who seemed to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29074Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29074Q\"></sup>pillars, perceived the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29074R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29074R\"></sup>grace that was given to me, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29074S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29074S\"></sup>gave the right hand of fellowship to Barnabas and me, that we should go to the Gentiles and they to the circumcised.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Only, they asked us to remember the poor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29075T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29075T\"></sup>the very thing I was eager to do.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29076U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29076U\"></sup>when Cephas came to Antioch, I opposed him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29076V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29076V\"></sup>to his face, because he stood condemned.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For before certain men came from James, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29077W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29077W\"></sup>he was eating with the Gentiles; but when they came he drew back and separated himself, fearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29077X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29077X\"></sup>the circumcision party.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the rest of the Jews acted hypocritically along with him, so that even Barnabas was led astray by their hypocrisy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when I saw that their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29079Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29079Y\"></sup>conduct was not in step with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29079Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29079Z\"></sup>the truth of the gospel, I said to Cephas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29079AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29079AA\"></sup>before them all, “If you, though a Jew, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29079AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29079AB\"></sup>live like a Gentile and not like a Jew, how can you force the Gentiles to live like Jews?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>We ourselves are Jews by birth and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29080AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29080AC\"></sup>Gentile sinners;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>yet we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29081AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29081AD\"></sup>a person is not justified by works of the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29081AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29081AE\"></sup>but through faith in Jesus Christ, so we also have believed in Christ Jesus, in order to be justified by faith in Christ and not by works of the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29081AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29081AF\"></sup>because by works of the law no one will be justified.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But if, in our endeavor to be justified in Christ, we too were found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29082AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29082AG\"></sup>to be sinners, is Christ then a servant of sin? Certainly not!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For if I rebuild what I tore down, I prove myself to be a transgressor.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For through the law I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29084AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29084AH\"></sup>died to the law, so that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29084AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29084AI\"></sup>live to God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29085AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29085AJ\"></sup>crucified with Christ. It is no longer I who live, but Christ who lives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29085AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29085AK\"></sup>in me. And the life I now live in the flesh I live by faith in the Son of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29085AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29085AL\"></sup>who loved me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29085AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29085AM\"></sup>gave himself for me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I do not nullify the grace of God, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29086AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29086AN\"></sup>if righteousness were through the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29086AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29086AO\"></sup>then Christ died for no purpose."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>O foolish Galatians! Who has bewitched you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29087A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29087A\"></sup>It was before your eyes that Jesus Christ was publicly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29087B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29087B\"></sup>portrayed as crucified.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let me ask you only this: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29088C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29088C\"></sup>Did you receive the Spirit by works of the law or by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29088D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29088D\"></sup>hearing with faith?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Are you so foolish? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29089E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29089E\"></sup>Having begun by the Spirit, are you now being perfected by the flesh?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29090F\"></sup>Did you suffer so many things in vain—if indeed it was in vain?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Does he who supplies the Spirit to you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29091G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29091G\"></sup>works miracles among you do so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29091H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29091H\"></sup>by works of the law, or by hearing with faith—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29092I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29092I\"></sup>Abraham “believed God, and it was counted to him as righteousness”?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Know then that it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29093J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29093J\"></sup>those of faith who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29093K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29093K\"></sup>the sons of Abraham.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the Scripture, foreseeing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29094L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29094L\"></sup>God would justify the Gentiles by faith, preached the gospel beforehand to Abraham, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29094M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29094M\"></sup>“In you shall all the nations be blessed.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So then, those who are of faith are blessed along with Abraham, the man of faith.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For all who rely on works of the law are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29096N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29096N\"></sup>under a curse; for it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29096O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29096O\"></sup>“Cursed be everyone who does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29096P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29096P\"></sup>abide by all things written in the Book of the Law, and do them.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now it is evident that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29097Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29097Q\"></sup>no one is justified before God by the law, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29097R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29097R\"></sup>“The righteous shall live by faith.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But the law is not of faith, rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29098S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29098S\"></sup>“The one who does them shall live by them.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29099T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29099T\"></sup>redeemed us from the curse of the law by becoming a curse for us—for it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29099U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29099U\"></sup>“Cursed is everyone who is hanged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29099V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29099V\"></sup>on a tree”—",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>so that in Christ Jesus the blessing of Abraham might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29100W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29100W\"></sup>come to the Gentiles, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29100X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29100X\"></sup>we might receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29100Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29100Y\"></sup>the promised Spirit through faith.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29101Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29101Z\"></sup>To give a human example, brothers: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29101AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29101AA\"></sup>even with a man-made covenant, no one annuls it or adds to it once it has been ratified.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29102AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29102AB\"></sup>the promises were made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29102AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29102AC\"></sup>to Abraham and to his offspring. It does not say, “And to offsprings,” referring to many, but referring to one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29102AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29102AD\"></sup>“And to your offspring,” who is Christ.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This is what I mean: the law, which came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29103AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29103AE\"></sup>430 years afterward, does not annul a covenant previously ratified by God, so as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29103AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29103AF\"></sup>to make the promise void.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For if the inheritance comes by the law, it no longer comes by promise; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29104AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29104AG\"></sup>God gave it to Abraham by a promise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Why then the law? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29105AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29105AH\"></sup>It was added because of transgressions, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29105AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29105AI\"></sup>until the offspring should come to whom the promise had been made, and it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29105AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29105AJ\"></sup>put in place through angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29105AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29105AK\"></sup>by an intermediary.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29106AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29106AL\"></sup>an intermediary implies more than one, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29106AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29106AM\"></sup>God is one.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Is the law then contrary to the promises of God? Certainly not! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29107AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29107AN\"></sup>if a law had been given that could give life, then righteousness would indeed be by the law.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But the Scripture <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29108AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29108AO\"></sup>imprisoned everything under sin, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29108AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29108AP\"></sup>the promise by faith in Jesus Christ might be given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29108AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29108AQ\"></sup>to those who believe.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Now before faith came, we were held captive under the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29109AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29109AR\"></sup>imprisoned until the coming faith would be revealed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29110AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29110AS\"></sup>the law was our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29110AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29110AT\"></sup>guardian until Christ came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29110AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29110AU\"></sup>in order that we might be justified by faith.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But now that faith has come, we are no longer under a guardian,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for in Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29112AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29112AV\"></sup>you are all sons of God, through faith.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For as many of you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29113AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29113AW\"></sup>were baptized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29113AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29113AX\"></sup>into Christ have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29113AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29113AY\"></sup>put on Christ.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29114AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29114AZ\"></sup>There is neither Jew nor Greek, there is neither slave nor free, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29114BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29114BA\"></sup>there is no male and female, for you are all one in Christ Jesus.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29115BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29115BB\"></sup>if you are Christ's, then you are Abraham's offspring, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29115BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29115BC\"></sup>heirs according to promise."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>I mean that the heir, as long as he is a child, is no different from a slave, though he is the owner of everything,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but he is under guardians and managers until the date set by his father.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the same way we also, when we were children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29118A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29118A\"></sup>were enslaved to the elementary principles of the world.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29119B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29119B\"></sup>when the fullness of time had come, God sent forth his Son, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29119C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29119C\"></sup>born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29119D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29119D\"></sup>of woman, born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29119E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29119E\"></sup>under the law,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29120F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29120F\"></sup>to redeem those who were under the law, so that we might receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29120G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29120G\"></sup>adoption as sons.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And because you are sons, God has sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29121H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29121H\"></sup>the Spirit of his Son into our hearts, crying, “Abba! Father!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So you are no longer a slave, but a son, and if a son, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29122I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29122I\"></sup>an heir through God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Formerly, when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29123J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29123J\"></sup>did not know God, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29123K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29123K\"></sup>were enslaved to those that by nature <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29123L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29123L\"></sup>are not gods.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But now that you have come to know God, or rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29124M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29124M\"></sup>to be known by God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29124N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29124N\"></sup>how can you turn back again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29124O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29124O\"></sup>the weak and worthless elementary principles of the world, whose slaves you want to be once more?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29125P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29125P\"></sup>You observe days and months and seasons and years!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I am afraid <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29126Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29126Q\"></sup>I may have labored over you in vain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29127R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29127R\"></sup>I entreat you, become as I am, for I also have become as you are. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29127S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29127S\"></sup>You did me no wrong.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You know it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29128T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29128T\"></sup>because of a bodily ailment that I preached the gospel to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29128U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29128U\"></sup>at first,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and though my condition was a trial to you, you did not scorn or despise me, but received me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29129V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29129V\"></sup>as an angel of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29129W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29129W\"></sup>as Christ Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>What then has become of your blessedness? For I testify to you that, if possible, you would have gouged out your eyes and given them to me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Have I then become your enemy by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29131X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29131X\"></sup>telling you the truth?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They make much of you, but for no good purpose. They want to shut you out, that you may make much of them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>It is always good to be made much of for a good purpose, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29133Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29133Y\"></sup>not only when I am present with you,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29134Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29134Z\"></sup>my little children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29134AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29134AA\"></sup>for whom I am again in the anguish of childbirth until Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29134AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29134AB\"></sup>is formed in you!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I wish I could be present with you now and change my tone, for I am perplexed about you.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Tell me, you who desire to be under the law, do you not listen to the law?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For it is written that Abraham had two sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29137AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29137AC\"></sup>one by a slave woman and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29137AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29137AD\"></sup>one by a free woman.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29138AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29138AE\"></sup>the son of the slave was born according to the flesh, while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29138AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29138AF\"></sup>the son of the free woman was born through promise.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now this may be interpreted allegorically: these women are two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29139AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29139AG\"></sup>covenants. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29139AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29139AH\"></sup>One is from Mount Sinai, bearing children for slavery; she is Hagar.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now Hagar is Mount Sinai in Arabia; she corresponds to the present Jerusalem, for she is in slavery with her children.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29141AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29141AI\"></sup>the Jerusalem above is free, and she is our mother.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29142AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29142AJ\"></sup>“Rejoice, O barren one who does not bear;break forth and cry aloud, you who are not in labor!For the children of the desolate one will be morethan those of the one who has a husband.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now you, brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29143AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29143AK\"></sup>like Isaac, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29143AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29143AL\"></sup>are children of promise.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But just as at that time he who was born according to the flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29144AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29144AM\"></sup>persecuted him who was born according to the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29144AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29144AN\"></sup>so also it is now.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But what does the Scripture say? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29145AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29145AO\"></sup>“Cast out the slave woman and her son, for the son of the slave woman shall not inherit with the son of the free woman.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So, brothers, we are not children of the slave but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29146AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29146AP\"></sup>of the free woman."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29147A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29147A\"></sup>freedom Christ has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29147B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29147B\"></sup>set us free; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29147C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29147C\"></sup>stand firm therefore, and do not submit again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29147D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29147D\"></sup>a yoke of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29147E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29147E\"></sup>slavery.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Look: I, Paul, say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29148F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29148F\"></sup>if you accept circumcision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29148G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29148G\"></sup>Christ will be of no advantage to you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I testify again to every man who accepts circumcision that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29149H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29149H\"></sup>he is obligated to keep the whole law.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29150I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29150I\"></sup>severed from Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29150J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29150J\"></sup>you who would be justified by the law; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29150K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29150K\"></sup>you have fallen away from grace.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For through the Spirit, by faith, we ourselves eagerly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29151L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29151L\"></sup>wait for the hope of righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For in Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29152M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29152M\"></sup>neither circumcision nor uncircumcision counts for anything, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29152N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29152N\"></sup>only faith working through love.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29153O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29153O\"></sup>You were running well. Who hindered you from obeying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29153P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29153P\"></sup>the truth?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>This persuasion is not from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29154Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29154Q\"></sup>him who calls you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29155R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29155R\"></sup>A little leaven leavens the whole lump.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29156S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29156S\"></sup>I have confidence in the Lord that you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29156T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29156T\"></sup>take no other view, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29156U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29156U\"></sup>the one who is troubling you will bear the penalty, whoever he is.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But if I, brothers, still preach circumcision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29157V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29157V\"></sup>why am I still being persecuted? In that case <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29157W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29157W\"></sup>the offense of the cross has been removed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I wish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29158X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29158X\"></sup>those who unsettle you would emasculate themselves!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For you were called to freedom, brothers. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29159Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29159Y\"></sup>Only do not use your freedom as an opportunity for the flesh, but through love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29159Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29159Z\"></sup>serve one another.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29160AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29160AA\"></sup>the whole law is fulfilled in one word: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29160AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29160AB\"></sup>“You shall love your neighbor as yourself.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29161AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29161AC\"></sup>bite and devour one another, watch out that you are not consumed by one another.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But I say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29162AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29162AD\"></sup>walk by the Spirit, and you will not gratify <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29162AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29162AE\"></sup>the desires of the flesh.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29163AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29163AF\"></sup>the desires of the flesh are against the Spirit, and the desires of the Spirit are against the flesh, for these are opposed to each other, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29163AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29163AG\"></sup>to keep you from doing the things you want to do.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But if you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29164AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29164AH\"></sup>led by the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29164AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29164AI\"></sup>you are not under the law.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29165AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29165AJ\"></sup>the works of the flesh are evident: sexual immorality, impurity, sensuality,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>idolatry, sorcery, enmity, strife, jealousy, fits of anger, rivalries, dissensions, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29166AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29166AK\"></sup>divisions,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>envy, drunkenness, orgies, and things like these. I warn you, as I warned you before, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29167AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29167AL\"></sup>those who do such things will not inherit the kingdom of God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29168AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29168AM\"></sup>the fruit of the Spirit is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29168AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29168AN\"></sup>love, joy, peace, patience, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29168AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29168AO\"></sup>kindness, goodness, faithfulness,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29169AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29169AP\"></sup>gentleness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29169AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29169AQ\"></sup>self-control; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29169AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29169AR\"></sup>against such things there is no law.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And those who belong to Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29170AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29170AS\"></sup>have crucified the flesh with its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29170AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29170AT\"></sup>passions and desires.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>If we live by the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29171AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29171AU\"></sup>let us also keep in step with the Spirit.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29172AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29172AV\"></sup>Let us not become conceited, provoking one another, envying one another."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29173A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29173A\"></sup>if anyone is caught in any transgression, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29173B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29173B\"></sup>you who are spiritual should restore him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29173C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29173C\"></sup>a spirit of gentleness. Keep watch on yourself, lest you too be tempted.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29174D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29174D\"></sup>Bear one another's burdens, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29174E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29174E\"></sup>so fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29174F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29174F\"></sup>the law of Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29175G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29175G\"></sup>if anyone thinks he is something, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29175H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29175H\"></sup>when he is nothing, he deceives himself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But let each one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29176I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29176I\"></sup>test his own work, and then his reason to boast will be in himself alone and not in his neighbor.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29177J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29177J\"></sup>each will have to bear his own load.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29178K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29178K\"></sup>Let the one who is taught the word share all good things with the one who teaches.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29179L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29179L\"></sup>Do not be deceived: God is not mocked, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29179M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29179M\"></sup>whatever one sows, that will he also reap.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29180N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29180N\"></sup>the one who sows to his own flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29180O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29180O\"></sup>will from the flesh reap corruption, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29180P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29180P\"></sup>the one who sows to the Spirit will from the Spirit reap eternal life.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29181Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29181Q\"></sup>let us not grow weary of doing good, for in due season we will reap, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29181R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29181R\"></sup>if we do not give up.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29182S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29182S\"></sup>as we have opportunity, let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29182T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29182T\"></sup>do good to everyone, and especially to those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29182U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29182U\"></sup>of the household of faith.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>See with what large letters I am writing to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29183V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29183V\"></sup>with my own hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29184W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29184W\"></sup>It is those who want to make a good showing in the flesh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29184X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29184X\"></sup>who would force you to be circumcised, and only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29184Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29184Y\"></sup>in order that they may not be persecuted for the cross of Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For even those who are circumcised do not themselves keep the law, but they desire to have you circumcised that they may boast in your flesh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But far be it from me to boast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29186Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29186Z\"></sup>except in the cross of our Lord Jesus Christ, by which the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29186AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29186AA\"></sup>has been crucified to me, and I to the world.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29187AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29187AB\"></sup>neither circumcision counts for anything, nor uncircumcision, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29187AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29187AC\"></sup>a new creation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And as for all who walk by this rule, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29188AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29188AD\"></sup>peace and mercy be upon them, and upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29188AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29188AE\"></sup>the Israel of God.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>From now on let no one cause me trouble, for I bear on my body the marks of Jesus.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29190AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29190AF\"></sup>The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29190AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29190AG\"></sup>with your spirit, brothers. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;